<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-44-0814 </DOCNO><TEXT>Describes operation of flotation concentrate dryers and reviews the problemof coal, coke and flotation concentrate drying. Characterizes the VenotPic, ROW-1 and ROW-2 dryers used in the mines of the Rybnicko-JastrzebskieCoal Company and their operation as well as new dryer designs. The wearmechanism and properties of the material used for dryer constructionare discussed. Work done on using Cr-Mn steels for flotation concentratedrying equipment is outlined. Field tests of dryers were carried outat the Maja, Moszczenica and Manifest Lipcowy mines.</TEXT></DOC>